Package org.dspace.identifier Description

Providers of durable unique identifiers (Handles, DOIs, etc.). Generally, subclasses of IdentifierProvider offer methods to create, delete, and resolve subclasses of Identifier. Classes outside this package should rely on IdentifierService to perform these operations using the most appropriate provider.
